# SegmentationFlow
This repository includes the following files.

--- CurveEvolution.m
This includes functions to 
1. create a plot of as a surface (height function) and a separate plot of its zero-crossings. 
2. curv
create a avi file to show curve evolution

--- SegmentationFlow.m
Simplified version of the Malladi-Sethian-Vemuri shape modeling flow to use curve evolution for segmentation

--- spiral.jpg
Image for curve evolution

--- beetle.jpg
Images for segmentatin flow